Look at yourself.

13
00:01:23,183 --> 00:01:24,932
<i>You like what you see.</i>

14
00:01:26,686 --> 00:01:28,436
Don't open the whole coat.

15
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:33,441
Just try and make it look like

16
