Very good, Cindy.

40
00:03:08,571 --> 00:03:10,738
Thank you very much, Cindy.

41
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:12,657
We'll let you know.

42
00:03:15,245 --> 00:03:18,212
<i>♪ If that's all ♪</i>

43
